    "However, they differ significantly in quadruple extraction performance.",
    "The T5-based method is more robust and produces higher quality results, while Chat-GPT has stronger generality and generalization ability, giving it an advantage in dialogue tasks.",
    "The T5-based method uses sequence-to-sequence mapping, making it flexible and scalable.",
    "This method usually involves pre-training and fine-tuning stages.",
